videos.headline: Vescovi helps No. 7 Vols grind it out vs. Ole Miss
videos.description: After scoring 22 points to help Tennessee hold off the Rebels for a 63-59 road win, Santiago Vescovi says he and his teammates know SEC play means it's a new season.
